WEBVTT

00:06.571 --> 00:07.964
[ SIGHS ]

00:07.964 --> 00:11.315
NOBODY'S EVER
HAPPY TO SEE ME.

00:11.315 --> 00:12.534
YOU'RE RIGHT.

00:12.534 --> 00:15.319
YOU HAVEN'T LOST
THE ATTITUDE.

00:15.319 --> 00:18.366
I REMEMBER THAT ABOUT YOU
FROM LAST SUMMER,

00:18.366 --> 00:21.586
WHEN YOU SHOT THE CITIZEN
DEAD IN HIS OWN HOME.

00:21.586 --> 00:24.720
I FIGURED
YOU'D BRING THAT UP.

00:24.720 --> 00:26.330
JUST SMALL TALK.

00:26.330 --> 00:27.810
HE ATTACKED ME
WITH A KNIFE.

00:27.810 --> 00:29.812
PROBABLY.

00:29.812 --> 00:31.683
I EXONERATED YOU.

00:31.683 --> 00:34.208
YEAH, 'CAUSE I ACTED
APPROPRIATELY.

00:34.208 --> 00:38.125
YOU TOOK OUT A $30,000 LOAN
FROM THE CREDIT UNION LAST WEEK.

00:38.125 --> 00:40.823
WHAT FOR?

00:40.823 --> 00:42.999
I DIDN'T REALIZE
MY FINANCIAL TRANSACTIONS

00:42.999 --> 00:44.609
NEEDED TO BE
APPROVED BY YOU.

00:44.609 --> 00:46.742
DID YOU TAKE THE MONEY OUT
FOR YOUR BROTHER?

00:46.742 --> 00:48.787
NO.

00:51.312 --> 00:54.837
LOOK, I'M TALKING TO YOU
AS A COURTESY.

00:54.837 --> 00:57.057
OKAY.

00:57.057 --> 00:59.233
YOU KNOW
HE'S A DIRTY MESS.

00:59.233 --> 01:02.018
MY BROTHER MIGHT HAVE
PERSONAL ISSUES,

01:02.018 --> 01:04.151
BUT HE'S A GOOD COP,
SO...

01:04.151 --> 01:06.153
I WISH YOU WERE RIGHT.
YOU'RE NOT.

01:06.153 --> 01:07.763
FIVE YEARS IN VICE?

01:07.763 --> 01:10.809
EVEN THE GOOD GUYS
CAN LOSE THEIR WAY.

01:10.809 --> 01:13.856
YOU DON'T KNOW
WHERE YOUR MONEY'S GOING.

01:13.856 --> 01:16.424
HE COULD TELL YOU
HE'S BEEN --

01:16.424 --> 01:18.643
OKAY, LET'S SAY GAMBLING
JUST AS AN EXAMPLE.

01:18.643 --> 01:20.950
WHAT IF
IT'S SOMETHING WORSE

01:20.950 --> 01:21.994
AND THE MONEY'S
TRACED BACK TO YOU?

01:21.994 --> 01:23.257
END OF YOUR CAREER.

01:23.257 --> 01:26.825
YOU GO TO JAIL
FOR CORRUPTION.

01:26.825 --> 01:29.176
YOU MAY NOT BE AS LUCKY
AS YOUR FATHER WAS.

01:32.222 --> 01:34.094
YOU'RE OVERSTEPPING
RIGHT NOW.

01:34.094 --> 01:36.096
SO ARE YOU.

01:38.141 --> 01:40.187
COME ON.
YOU'RE A SINGLE MOTHER.

01:40.187 --> 01:42.406
YOU CAN'T AFFORD TO
JEOPARDIZE YOUR LIVELIHOOD.

01:42.406 --> 01:44.756
YOU NEED TO STAY AWAY FROM
YOUR BROTHER FOR A WHILE

01:44.756 --> 01:49.239
UNTIL HE'S CLEARED UP...
OR HE ISN'T.

01:49.239 --> 01:51.676
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

01:51.676 --> 01:53.548
THAT'S MY FREE ADVICE.

01:53.548 --> 01:55.158
ARE WE DONE HERE?

01:58.509 --> 01:59.858
YES, I AM.

01:59.858 --> 02:03.123
KEEP ACTING APPROPRIATELY,
INSPECTOR.

02:05.255 --> 02:07.170
YOU CAN'T SAVE YOUR BROTHER
FROM HIMSELF.

02:07.170 --> 02:10.173
♪♪

02:22.098 --> 02:23.621
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

02:23.621 --> 02:24.970
[ INDISTINCT SHOUTING ]

02:24.970 --> 02:26.537
MS. NELSON,
HOW DO YOU FEEL

02:26.537 --> 02:28.452
ABOUT THE LASH BACK
YOU'RE GETTING?

02:28.452 --> 02:30.889
WHEN DID YOU FIND OUT
THE VIDEO WENT VIRAL?

02:30.889 --> 02:34.502
DID YOU MEAN
WHAT YOU SAID TO HOLLY?

02:34.502 --> 02:36.330
WILL YOUR WRECK
OF A HOME LIFE

02:36.330 --> 02:38.332
HAVE AN IMPACT ON YOU
IN COURT TODAY?

02:39.724 --> 02:40.769
NO.

02:40.769 --> 02:42.814
MS. NELSON?

02:42.814 --> 02:47.254
GOOD MORNING, GENTLEMEN.

02:47.254 --> 02:49.386
YOU ALL RIGHT?

02:49.386 --> 02:50.692
FINE.

02:50.692 --> 02:52.998
I JUST WANTED TO SAY PERSONALLY,
JAMIE,

02:52.998 --> 02:54.565
I'VE ALWAYS SUPPORTED
GAY MARRIAGE.

02:54.565 --> 02:56.872
I THINK THE LGBT COMMUNITY

02:56.872 --> 03:00.092
HAS THE ABSOLUTE RIGHT TO BE
AS MISERABLE AS THE REST OF US.

03:00.092 --> 03:01.833
I'VE HEARD IT BEFORE.

03:01.833 --> 03:03.444
WELL, IT DOESN'T MAKE ME
ANY LESS SINCERE.

03:03.444 --> 03:05.272
TELLS ME A LOT
ABOUT YOURMARRIAGE, MARIO.

03:05.272 --> 03:06.273
[ CHUCKLES ]

03:06.273 --> 03:08.013
[ DOOR OPENS ]

03:08.013 --> 03:10.755
♪♪

03:20.852 --> 03:22.680
SILENCE IN THE COURTROOM.

03:22.680 --> 03:23.855
ALL RISE.

03:23.855 --> 03:26.075
COURT IS NOW IN SESSION.

03:26.075 --> 03:28.033
THE HONORABLE MITCHELL ELLIS
PRESIDING.

03:28.033 --> 03:29.774
PLEASE SIT DOWN.

03:33.952 --> 03:35.606
YOU READY?

03:35.606 --> 03:39.915
TO TESTIFY FOR SOMEONE
WHO KILLED 18 PEOPLE?

03:39.915 --> 03:41.612
WHO TRIED TO KILL YOU?

03:41.612 --> 03:42.874
[ INHALES DEEPLY ]

03:42.874 --> 03:44.485
NOT READY.
[ SIGHS ]

03:44.485 --> 03:47.879
INSPECTOR, YOU'RE UP.

03:47.879 --> 03:49.185
[ Sighing ]
OH, I HATE THIS.

03:50.752 --> 03:54.321
HEY.

03:54.321 --> 03:56.192
I'LL SEE YOU UPSTAIRS.

03:56.192 --> 03:58.238
YEAH.

03:59.543 --> 04:02.242
NOW, DID THERE COME A TIME
AT POINT BONITA LIGHTHOUSE

04:02.242 --> 04:04.156
WHEN MR. RENTMAN
OFFERED TO SURRENDER

04:04.156 --> 04:05.506
TO YOU PERSONALLY,
INSPECTOR?

04:05.506 --> 04:06.637
YES.

04:06.637 --> 04:09.118
SPECIFICALLY YOU
AND ONLY YOU?

04:09.118 --> 04:10.554
YES.

04:10.554 --> 04:12.643
DID HE SAY WHY?

04:12.643 --> 04:16.212
HE SAID THAT
I WAS HIS PRINCESS.

04:16.212 --> 04:18.258
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT HE MEANT BY THAT?

04:18.258 --> 04:19.998
HE WAS REFERENCING
A VIDEO GAME

04:19.998 --> 04:22.000
THAT HE AND THE DEFENDANT
WERE ACTING OUT.

04:22.000 --> 04:24.220
WAS THAT GAME
"BAY CITY BULLETS"?

04:24.220 --> 04:25.700
YES.

04:25.700 --> 04:28.529
A SINGLE-PLAYER,
FIRST-PERSON-SHOOTER GAME

04:28.529 --> 04:30.313
THAT LAW ENFORCEMENT
DECRYPTED

04:30.313 --> 04:32.663
ON MR. RENTMAN'S
PERSONAL COMPUTER, CORRECT?

04:32.663 --> 04:34.230
CORRECT.

04:34.230 --> 04:36.319
IS THERE ANY EVIDENCE
THAT DUSTIN --

04:36.319 --> 04:39.801
SPECIFICALLY DUSTIN --
WAS RE-ENACTING THAT GAME?

04:41.629 --> 04:43.195
HE SHOT PEOPLE.

04:43.195 --> 04:47.025
DID MR. RENTMAN EVER MENTION
DUSTIN TO YOU IN ANY WAY?

04:47.025 --> 04:48.636
NO.

04:48.636 --> 04:53.684
WHERE WAS DUSTIN DURING
THE EVENTS AT THE LIGHTHOUSE?

04:53.684 --> 04:55.338
HE WAS HOSPITALIZED

04:55.338 --> 04:57.035
WITH INJURIES THAT HE SUSTAINED
DURING HIS ARREST.

04:57.035 --> 05:00.909
SO MR. RENTMAN WAS ACTING ALONE,
WASN'T HE?

05:00.909 --> 05:02.476
MS. NELSON,

05:02.476 --> 05:05.130
REDUNDANCY IS NOBODY'S FRIEND
IN THE COURTROOM.

05:05.130 --> 05:07.568
I'LL REPHRASE FOR YOU, JUDGE.
WAS MR. RENTMAN ALONE?

05:07.568 --> 05:11.485
NO, HE TOOK A CLASSMATE HOSTAGE.
HER NAME WAS BARBIE SANFORD.

05:11.485 --> 05:13.443
WHAT, IF ANYTHING,
DID YOU DO?

05:13.443 --> 05:17.186
I OFFERED TO EXCHANGE MYSELF
FOR THE HOSTAGE.

05:17.186 --> 05:18.405
HE ACCEPTED.

05:18.405 --> 05:20.537
WHAT HAPPENED
AT THE EXCHANGE POINT?

05:20.537 --> 05:22.844
HE RENEGED,
REFUSED TO RELEASE HER.

05:22.844 --> 05:24.498
THE GAME ONLY ENDS

05:24.498 --> 05:26.369
WHEN THE HERO
RESCUES THE PRINCESS.

05:26.369 --> 05:28.458
WHAT DID MR. RENTMAN SAY?

05:28.458 --> 05:32.549
HE SAID
HE WAS THE BAD GUY.

05:32.549 --> 05:36.118
HE SAID THAT I WAS THE ONLY ONE
THAT COULD END THE GAME

05:36.118 --> 05:38.729
AND THAT THE GAME ALWAYS ENDED
THE SAME WAY.

05:38.729 --> 05:40.383
DID YOU RESPOND?

05:40.383 --> 05:41.515
I DID.

05:41.515 --> 05:44.735
I SAID
THAT IT DOESN'T HAVE TO.

05:44.735 --> 05:47.477
IS THAT WHEN HE AIMED THE GUN
AT YOUR HEAD?

05:47.477 --> 05:49.697
[ SCREAMS ]

05:49.697 --> 05:51.089
YES.

05:51.089 --> 05:53.353
AND CAUSED A POLICE SNIPER
TO END THE GAME?

05:56.486 --> 05:58.880
IT WASN'T A GAME

05:58.880 --> 06:01.665
TO THE 18 VICTIMS
THAT LOST THEIR LIVES, MA'AM.

06:01.665 --> 06:05.016
YOU'RE AN EXPERIENCED
POLICE OFFICER

06:05.016 --> 06:08.629
WITH 14 YEARS IN THE DEPARTMENT,
6 OF THOSE IN HOMICIDE.

06:08.629 --> 06:11.632
AND YET MR. RENTMAN
MANAGED TO MANIPULATE YOU

06:11.632 --> 06:15.244
INTO DOING EXACTLY
WHAT HE WANTED, DIDN'T HE?

06:15.244 --> 06:19.509
HE MADE YOU CARRY OUT HIS PLAN,
DIDN'T HE?

06:21.293 --> 06:24.819
I DON'T KNOW
WHAT HIS PLAN WAS.

06:24.819 --> 06:27.778
BUT I'M A COP.

06:27.778 --> 06:31.303
AND IF I COULD STOP HIM FROM
KILLING ANOTHER INNOCENT VICTIM,

06:31.303 --> 06:33.915
THAT'S WHAT I WAS GONNA DO.

06:39.311 --> 06:42.227
THE DEFENSE CALLS
DR. FRANK RENTMAN.

06:42.227 --> 06:46.057
NOW, AS A NEUROSCIENTIST WITH A
SPECIALIZATION IN SOCIOPATHY --

06:46.057 --> 06:47.407
I'M CONSIDERED
ONE OF THE FOREMOST

06:47.407 --> 06:50.410
EXPERTS IN THE FIELD,
WORLD-WIDE.

06:50.410 --> 06:53.978
YOUR SON ALFRED WAS
ALSO YOUR PATIENT, WASN'T HE?

06:53.978 --> 06:55.197
YES.

06:55.197 --> 06:57.286
WHAT WAS YOUR
CLINICAL DIAGNOSIS

06:57.286 --> 06:59.070
OF HIS MENTAL CONDITION,
DOCTOR?

06:59.070 --> 07:02.291
ALFRED DISPLAYED
THE BRAIN-IMAGING PATTERN

07:02.291 --> 07:06.077
AND BIOLOGICAL MARKERS
OF A CATEGORICAL SOCIOPATH,

07:06.077 --> 07:10.125
ALONG WITH A DOCUMENTED GENETIC
HISTORY OF SCHIZOTYPAL BEHAVIOR.

07:10.125 --> 07:13.433
WHAT SOCIOPATHIC TRAITS DID YOU
SPECIFICALLY SEE IN YOUR SON?

07:13.433 --> 07:16.871
HIS LACK
OF EMOTIONAL EMPATHY.

07:16.871 --> 07:19.482
HIS AGGRESSIVE NARCISSISM.

07:19.482 --> 07:23.530
HIS RELIANCE ON
DECEIT AND MANIPULATION.

07:23.530 --> 07:28.360
HIS INABILITY TO FEEL FEAR
OR GUILT OR ANY KIND OF REMORSE.

07:28.360 --> 07:31.929
ALFRED MANIFESTED
THE FULL-BLOWN DISORDER.

07:31.929 --> 07:33.627
WAS HE SMART?

07:33.627 --> 07:37.761
ON THE STANFORD-BINET
INTELLIGENCE SCALE,

07:37.761 --> 07:40.285
ALFRED RANKED
IN THE HIGHEST RANGE --

07:40.285 --> 07:42.592
"VERY GIFTED."

07:42.592 --> 07:44.333
WAS HE PERSUASIVE?

07:44.333 --> 07:48.729
MOST SOCIOPATHS USE DECEIT
AND MANIPULATION

07:48.729 --> 07:51.427
TO GET WHAT THEY WANT.

07:51.427 --> 07:54.778
ALFRED COULD BE...
CHARMING.

07:54.778 --> 07:56.606
COULD HE HAVE PERSUADED

07:56.606 --> 08:00.218
AN EMOTIONALLY DAMAGED TEENAGER
SUCH AS DUSTIN

08:00.218 --> 08:03.744
TO COMMIT ACTS HE WOULD NEVER
HAVE IMAGINED WITHOUT ALFRED?

08:03.744 --> 08:05.528
ABSOLUTELY.

08:05.528 --> 08:07.748
WERE YOU AFRAID
OF ALFRED?

08:10.881 --> 08:15.233
THERE IS NO CURE
FOR SOCIOPATHY.

08:15.233 --> 08:17.932
WERE YOU AFRAID
OF YOUR SON?

08:20.848 --> 08:23.633
HE WAS A MONSTER.

08:23.633 --> 08:27.158
[ SPECTATORS MURMURING ]

08:27.158 --> 08:32.076
DR. RENTMAN, DID YOU EVER
SEEK OUTSIDE HELP FOR YOUR BOY?

08:32.076 --> 08:33.295
A THERAPIST?

08:33.295 --> 08:35.079
A CHILD PSYCHOLOGIST?

08:35.079 --> 08:36.385
ANYONE AT ALL?

08:36.385 --> 08:39.736
THERAPY CAN'T
CHANGE BRAIN PATTERNS, SIR.

08:39.736 --> 08:41.695
SO YOUR ANSWER IS "NO"?

08:41.695 --> 08:45.916
I KNEW IT WOULDN'T MAKE
ANY DIFFERENCE TO HIS PROGNOSIS.

08:45.916 --> 08:47.265
BEFORE THE SHOOTINGS,

08:47.265 --> 08:49.398
DID YOU EVER
REPORT YOUR SON AS A DANGER

08:49.398 --> 08:51.400
TO THE HEALTH AND SAFETY
OF OTHERS?

08:51.400 --> 08:55.360
YOU'RE TRYING TO BLAME ME
FOR WHAT HAPPENED.

08:55.360 --> 08:56.971
IT'S NOT MY FAULT.

08:56.971 --> 08:59.582
NOT MY QUESTION,
DR. RENTMAN.

08:59.582 --> 09:01.192
MY QUESTION IS,

09:01.192 --> 09:03.107
DID YOU EVER
REPORT YOUR SON

09:03.107 --> 09:06.458
AS POSING A THREAT TO THE HEALTH
AND SAFETY OF ANYONE ELSE

09:06.458 --> 09:09.287
BEFORE HE HELPED THE DEFENDANT
MURDER 18 PEOPLE?

09:09.287 --> 09:11.072
NO, I DID NOT.

09:11.072 --> 09:14.684
THE BOY YOU DESCRIBED AS
A "SOCIOPATH" AND A "MONSTER"?

09:14.684 --> 09:20.168
SOME GREAT LEADERS
DISPLAY SOCIOPATHIC TRAITS.

09:20.168 --> 09:24.781
JOHN F. KENNEDY, BILL CLINTON,
STEVE JOBS, FOR EXAMPLE.

09:24.781 --> 09:28.089
DR. RENTMAN, THIS IS
A COURTROOM, NOT A CLASSROOM.

09:28.089 --> 09:31.266
PLEASE JUST ANSWER
THE QUESTIONS YOU'VE BEEN ASKED.

09:31.266 --> 09:34.312
PLEASE.

09:34.312 --> 09:35.749
MY ANSWER IS THAT

09:35.749 --> 09:39.187
MOST SOCIOPATHS DO NOT
COMMIT MURDERS, OBVIOUSLY.

09:41.276 --> 09:42.973
DID YOU EVER MEET
DUSTIN MAKER?

09:42.973 --> 09:44.496
NO.

09:44.496 --> 09:47.238
DID YOU EVER MEET
ANY OF YOUR SON'S FRIENDS?

09:47.238 --> 09:49.763
I DIDN'T KNOW
HE HAD ANY FRIENDS.

09:49.763 --> 09:52.504
THEN YOU DON'T KNOW WHO EXERTED
INFLUENCE ON HIM, DO YOU?

09:56.030 --> 09:57.727
MY SON
WAS NOT A FOLLOWER.

09:57.727 --> 10:02.123
BECAUSE HE WAS FOLLOWING THE
LEAD OF THAT MAN INSTEAD OF YOU.

10:04.995 --> 10:06.997
I HAVE NO MORE QUESTIONS
FOR THIS WITNESS, YOUR HONOR.

10:06.997 --> 10:11.045
[ SPECTATORS MURMURING ]

10:11.045 --> 10:12.437
MS. NELSON,
CAN YOU COMMENT

10:12.437 --> 10:14.178
ABOUT MR. RENTMAN'S TESTIMONY,
PLEASE?

10:14.178 --> 10:15.615
MA'AM?

10:15.615 --> 10:17.486
T-TAKE THE NEXT ONE,
OKAY?

10:17.486 --> 10:19.880
NO OBJECTIONS
DURING CROSS?

10:19.880 --> 10:21.533
NO REDIRECT?
[ CHUCKLES ]

10:21.533 --> 10:23.579
DIFFERENT PLAYS
IN A BENCH TRIAL.

10:23.579 --> 10:25.102
BUT -- BUT THERE'S --
THERE'S STILL THE MEDIA,

10:25.102 --> 10:26.190
STILL THE PUBLIC.

10:26.190 --> 10:27.322
WHO CARES?

10:27.322 --> 10:29.019
ONE PERSON MATTERS --
JUDGE ELLIS.

10:29.019 --> 10:31.152
IS HE GONNA DIRECT HIMSELF
TO DISREGARD

10:31.152 --> 10:33.589
IMPROPER CHARACTERIZATION
IN THE QUESTION? NO.

10:33.589 --> 10:36.244
IS HE GONNA TELL SILETTI TO SAVE
THE RHETORIC FOR HIS CLOSING?

10:36.244 --> 10:37.375
HE IS NOT.

10:37.375 --> 10:39.639
[ CHUCKLES ]
BUT RENTMAN HURT US.

10:39.639 --> 10:42.206
HE WAS PERFECT.

10:42.206 --> 10:44.339
ELLIS DIDN'T LIKE HIM.

10:44.339 --> 10:46.254
NO.

10:46.254 --> 10:47.385
BUT HE BELIEVED HIM.

10:47.385 --> 10:49.039
[ ELEVATOR BELL DINGS ]

10:49.039 --> 10:51.476
SHIT, A FATHER LIKE THAT
COULD HAVE MADE MEPSYCHO.

10:53.957 --> 10:56.438
HOW MUCH DO YOU THINK
HE REALLY KNOWS ABOUT JUNIOR?

10:56.438 --> 10:59.267
GUYS LIKE TORRES --

10:59.267 --> 11:02.879
HE'S LIKE A HUNTING DOG,
AND ONCE HE CATCHES A SCENT,

11:02.879 --> 11:04.664
HE STAYS ON THAT TRAIL.

11:04.664 --> 11:05.839
SAME AS US.

11:05.839 --> 11:08.015
YEAH.

11:08.015 --> 11:09.494
YOU KNOW,
HE DIDN'T HAVE TO WARN YOU.

11:09.494 --> 11:11.671
THAT WAS LIKE A FAVOR.

11:11.671 --> 11:13.629
IT'S GOOD TO KNOW
SOMEBODY AT MANAGEMENT CONTROL

11:13.629 --> 11:16.458
THAT HAS A HEART
FOR COPS.

11:16.458 --> 11:18.982
YOU THINK WE SHOULD BACK OFF?
PLEASE, NO, YOU DON'T.

11:18.982 --> 11:22.246
WELL, YOU HAVE
MORE AT RISK THAN I DO.

11:22.246 --> 11:23.987
WE COULD GO TO KOTO,

11:23.987 --> 11:25.597
SEE IF HE'LL GIVE YOU
A REASSIGNMENT,

11:25.597 --> 11:28.470
SEE IF
HE'LL FIREWALL YOU.

11:28.470 --> 11:35.390
SARAH, WALT,
CALEB, CRIOLLA.

11:35.390 --> 11:38.262
FOUR DEAD COPS, AND NOW
MY BROTHER'S NEXT ON THE LIST.

11:38.262 --> 11:41.962
WE CAN BREAK THE UNION, TERRY,
WHICH DOESN'T DESERVE THE NAME.

11:41.962 --> 11:43.877
WE CAN PROVE
WHAT THEY DID.

11:43.877 --> 11:45.052
WE CAN STOP THEM.

11:46.967 --> 11:48.751
I'M NOT PLAYING IT SAFE.

11:48.751 --> 11:50.013
I'M NOT.

11:52.581 --> 11:53.669
ARE YOU IN?

11:53.669 --> 11:56.716
YOU KNOW I AM.

12:03.287 --> 12:04.114
INSPECTORS.

12:04.114 --> 12:05.246
HEY.
HEY.

12:05.246 --> 12:06.290
WHAT'S GOING ON,
BURNSIDE?

12:06.290 --> 12:07.335
UH, A LOT.

12:07.335 --> 12:09.293
SO, A COUPLE DAYS AGO,

12:09.293 --> 12:11.861
UH, SOME MED STUDENTS WERE
DOING LIVER RESEARCH AT UCSF,

12:11.861 --> 12:13.863
AND THEY PULL
A JOHN DOE CADAVER,

12:13.863 --> 12:16.387
AND IT TURNS OUT TO BE THIS KID
XAVIER FURNESS.

12:16.387 --> 12:18.999
OKAY.
XA-- DON'T KNOW WHO THAT IS.MNH-MNH.

12:18.999 --> 12:21.828
XAVIER FURNESS WAS A GUNSHOT
VICTIM ABOUT SIX WEEKS AGO.

12:21.828 --> 12:22.916
HIS LIVER WAS FINE,

12:22.916 --> 12:24.178
BUT APPARENTLY THERE WAS

12:24.178 --> 12:25.962
SOME CONFUSION
WITH TOE TAGS,

12:25.962 --> 12:29.270
AND...XAVIER GOT REROUTED.

12:29.270 --> 12:32.360
HUH. WELL, I GUESS IT'S BETTER
THAN BEING STOLEN, RIGHT?

12:32.360 --> 12:33.883
YEAH.

12:33.883 --> 12:35.885
JALIL THOMPSON.
THAT WAS VERY WELL PLAYED.

12:35.885 --> 12:37.844
UH, ACTUALLY,
JALIL WASN'T STOLEN.

12:37.844 --> 12:39.802
JALIL WAS BURIED
IN XAVIER'S GRAVE.

12:39.802 --> 12:40.847
WHAT?

12:40.847 --> 12:42.196
UH, IT WAS
A CLOSED CASKET,

12:42.196 --> 12:43.806
SO THE FAMILY
DIDN'T KNOW.

12:43.806 --> 12:46.504
JALIL SOMEHOW ENDS UP
WITH XAVIER'S TOE TAG.

12:46.504 --> 12:49.464
XAVIER ENDS UP
WITH THE REST OF THE JOHN DOES.

12:49.464 --> 12:52.336
SO WE END UP EXHUMING JALIL
THIS MORNING,

12:52.336 --> 12:55.165
AND...I END UP TELLING YOU
ALL THIS STUFF

12:55.165 --> 12:56.123
'CAUSE I THINK
YOU SHOULD KNOW.

12:56.123 --> 12:57.385
HMM.

12:57.385 --> 13:00.605
AND...
LET THE LAWSUITS BEGIN,

13:00.605 --> 13:02.564
WHICH WILL BE LOTS OF FUN.

13:02.564 --> 13:04.653
YOU OKAY?

13:04.653 --> 13:06.350
NOT REALLY.

13:07.351 --> 13:09.440
Jamie: AND WHILE YOU WERE
COMPLETING YOUR RESIDENCY

13:09.440 --> 13:11.747
AT THE PLEASANTON MEDICAL
CENTER, DID YOU HAVE OCCASION

13:11.747 --> 13:13.575
TO TREAT DUSTIN MAKER
IN THE EMERGENCY ROOM?

13:13.575 --> 13:14.794
YES, I DID.

13:14.794 --> 13:17.405
WHAT WERE
THE CIRCUMSTANCES?

13:17.405 --> 13:19.755
DUSTIN WAS
A 6-YEAR-OLD CHILD

13:19.755 --> 13:21.583
WHO PRESENTED WITH
A SPIRAL FRACTURE

13:21.583 --> 13:24.847
OF THE DISTAL RADIUS BONE --
HIS FOREARM --

13:24.847 --> 13:26.893
CAUSED BY WHAT THE
ACCOMPANYING FAMILY MEMBER SAID

13:26.893 --> 13:29.025
WAS AN ACCIDENT
IN THE MACHINE SHOP AT HOME.

13:29.025 --> 13:31.898
DO YOU REMEMBER
WHO THE FAMILY MEMBER WAS?

13:31.898 --> 13:34.552
YES.
I CHECKED MY NOTES.

13:34.552 --> 13:37.599
HIS UNCLE, MR. BEAU RENELL,
BROUGHT THE BOY TO THE E.R.

13:37.599 --> 13:41.516
YOU KEPT YOUR NOTES FROM
YOUR RESIDENCY 12 YEARS AGO?

13:41.516 --> 13:43.910
FOR THIS PARTICULAR PATIENT, I
MADE SURE THAT I KEPT THEM, YES.

13:43.910 --> 13:45.563
WHY?

13:45.563 --> 13:47.522
'CAUSE I DON'T BELIEVE
THE INJURY WAS ACCIDENTAL.

13:47.522 --> 13:49.263
IT WAS CONSISTENT WITH

13:49.263 --> 13:52.222
DELIBERATE PHYSICAL ABUSE
OF A CHILD.

13:52.222 --> 13:54.137
DID YOU NOTIFY ANYONE?

13:54.137 --> 13:58.141
I REPORTED IT TO MY SUPERVISORS,
AND I CALLED THE POLICE.

13:58.141 --> 14:01.753
WAS ANY ACTION TAKEN
THAT YOU KNOW OF?

14:01.753 --> 14:03.712
NO.
NONE AT ALL.

14:03.712 --> 14:06.367
IN A SMALL TOWN LIKE PLEASANTON,
THEY DON'T HAVE

14:06.367 --> 14:09.109
THE SAME INVESTIGATIVE RESOURCES
OF AN URBAN AREA.

14:09.109 --> 14:13.330
DID YOU TELL DUSTIN'S PARENTS
THAT THE INJURY INDICATED ABUSE?

14:13.330 --> 14:16.856
NO.
'CAUSE I NEVER MET THEM.

14:16.856 --> 14:20.729
THEY FAXED THEIR PERMISSION
FOR THE SURGICAL REPAIR.

14:20.729 --> 14:23.645
I PHONED THE CONTACT NUMBER
ON THE FAX,

14:23.645 --> 14:25.516
BUT NEITHER ONE OF THEM
EVER GOT BACK TO ME.

14:25.516 --> 14:30.304
NEITHER ONE OF THEM
EVEN SHOWED UP AT THE HOSPITAL.

14:35.265 --> 14:37.833
DID DUSTIN
ASK FOR HIS PARENTS?

14:40.227 --> 14:43.012
HE CRIED FOR HIS MOM
IN THE OPERATING ROOM

14:43.012 --> 14:45.536
BEFORE THE ANESTHESIA
TOOK EFFECT.

14:49.192 --> 14:51.151
I NEVER FORGOT
ABOUT THAT LITTLE BOY.

14:57.722 --> 14:59.463
HOW OLD WERE YOU AT THE TIME,
DR. LEVIN?

14:59.463 --> 15:02.118
I WAS 27.

15:02.118 --> 15:05.252
FIRST-YEAR SURGICAL RESIDENT,
YES?

15:05.252 --> 15:06.253
YES.

15:06.253 --> 15:07.732
BRAND-NEW DOCTOR

15:07.732 --> 15:09.386
WITH VERY LITTLE EXPERIENCE
UNDER YOUR WHITE COAT.

15:09.386 --> 15:10.822
ISN'T THAT TRUE?

15:10.822 --> 15:12.650
DUSTIN WAS THE FIRST CASE
OF CHILD ABUSE

15:12.650 --> 15:14.478
I HAD EVER TREATED,
YES.

15:14.478 --> 15:17.351
VERY SADLY, NOT THE LAST IN
MY CAREER AS A TRAUMA SURGEON.

15:17.351 --> 15:19.222
A SPIRAL FRACTURE
LIKE HIS

15:19.222 --> 15:22.573
CAN ONLY BE CAUSED WITH
FORCEFUL TWISTING -- BY TORQUE.

15:22.573 --> 15:25.228
IT'S A VERY COMMON ABUSE INJURY
TO CHILDREN.

15:25.228 --> 15:27.187
I-I'VE SEEN IT
FAR TOO OFTEN.

15:27.187 --> 15:31.713
ACCIDENTALLY FALLING
ON AN OUTSTRETCHED ARM

15:31.713 --> 15:33.933
CAN ALSO CAUSE
A SPIRAL FRACTURE.

15:33.933 --> 15:35.238
ISN'T THAT CORRECT?

15:35.238 --> 15:36.892
YES.

15:36.892 --> 15:39.155
IN FACT, ISN'T THAT
ONE OF THE MOST COMMON

15:39.155 --> 15:41.375
ACCIDENTAL INJURIES
FOR CHILDREN OVER 5?

15:41.375 --> 15:42.724
YES, BUT --

15:42.724 --> 15:43.899
YOU DIDN'T LIKE HIS UNCLE BEAU,
DID YOU?

15:43.899 --> 15:45.031
Jamie:
OBJECTION, YOUR HONOR.

15:45.031 --> 15:46.380
DR. LEVIN'S
PERSONAL FEELINGS

15:46.380 --> 15:47.990
ARE NOT RELEVANT
TO HIS TESTIMONY.

15:47.990 --> 15:50.297
UNLESS THE WITNESS'S ANTIPATHY
FOR THE PATIENT'S FAMILY

15:50.297 --> 15:52.168
COLORED HIS INTERPRETATION
OF THE INJURY.

15:52.168 --> 15:54.518
ANTIPATHY HAS NOT
BEEN ESTABLISHED, JUDGE.

15:54.518 --> 15:56.694
YOUR HONOR, IF YOU WILL
PERMIT THE WITNESS TO ANSWER --

15:56.694 --> 16:00.350
I DO NOT NEED TO HEAR
THAT ANSWER TO THAT QUESTION.

16:00.350 --> 16:02.657
I'LL SUSTAIN THE OBJECTION.

16:04.267 --> 16:07.531
THEN I HAVE NO MORE
QUESTIONS OF ANY VALUE

16:07.531 --> 16:09.316
FOR THIS WITNESS,
YOUR HONOR.

16:11.274 --> 16:13.450
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ]

16:13.450 --> 16:15.235
COME TALK TO US.

16:27.334 --> 16:29.336
WHAT'S GOING ON?

16:29.336 --> 16:31.251
TORRES
IS HOT TO SKIN YOU.

16:31.251 --> 16:33.035
WELL, MANAGEMENT CONTROL
IS A PAPER CUT

16:33.035 --> 16:34.384
COMPARED TO
WHAT'S GOING ON.

16:34.384 --> 16:35.777
WELL, NOT FOR HILDY.

16:36.821 --> 16:38.301
TORRES CALLED ME IN.

16:38.301 --> 16:40.086
DID HE LEAN ON YOU?

16:40.086 --> 16:42.566
MORE LIKE
A COURTESY WARNING.

16:42.566 --> 16:45.004
[ SIGHS ]
GUY'S AN ASSHOLE.

16:45.004 --> 16:46.744
LOOK, I'M NOT GONNA LET YOU
GO DOWN FOR ME, OKAY?

16:46.744 --> 16:48.181
I'M GIVING YOU
BACK THE MONEY.

16:48.181 --> 16:49.791
JUNIOR, HOW ARE YOU GONNA
PAY THE UNION BACK

16:49.791 --> 16:51.358
WHAT YOU OWE THEM?I'LL FIGURE IT OUT.

16:51.358 --> 16:52.620
MY FAULT, MY FIX.

16:52.620 --> 16:54.230
JUNIOR,
I WAS YOUR LAST RESORT.

16:54.230 --> 16:56.102
THAT'S THE ONLY REASON
YOU CAME TO ME.

16:56.102 --> 16:58.147
WHAT IS ONE MORE DEAD COP
TO THEM AT THIS POINT?

16:58.147 --> 16:59.540
IT'S NOTHING.

16:59.540 --> 17:01.542
SHE'S RIGHT.
YOU GOT TO DELIVER THAT MONEY.

17:01.542 --> 17:03.152
TERRY, THIS IS BETWEEN
MY SISTER AND I, OKAY?

17:03.152 --> 17:04.719
EASY.

17:04.719 --> 17:06.938
WE'RE GONNA
FOLLOW THE MONEY.

17:06.938 --> 17:09.115
ON OUR OWN TIME,
OFF THE BOOKS.

17:09.115 --> 17:10.159
NO FOOTPRINT.

17:10.159 --> 17:11.682
WE'RE GONNA
LET THE MONEY

17:11.682 --> 17:14.033
TAKE US ALL THE WAY
UP TO THE HEAD MAN.

17:15.686 --> 17:17.688
WE'RE GONNA
PULL THE WHOLE THING APART.

17:17.688 --> 17:19.516
YOU GUYS ARE CRAZY.

17:19.516 --> 17:22.258
[ SIGHS ]

17:22.258 --> 17:24.826
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

17:24.826 --> 17:26.175
WHO IS IT?

17:26.175 --> 17:27.829
Holly: ME.

17:34.966 --> 17:36.925
ARE YOU ALONE?

17:36.925 --> 17:38.666
YES.

17:44.367 --> 17:47.762
I CAME TO SAY
I AM SORRY ABOUT WHAT HAPPENED.

17:47.762 --> 17:49.155
I FEEL TERRIBLE.

17:49.155 --> 17:50.982
I BROUGHT IT ON MYSELF.

17:50.982 --> 17:53.550
[ CHUCKLES ]
I LOST MY GRIP.

17:53.550 --> 17:57.598
I SAID AWFUL THINGS TO YOU
THAT I DIDN'T EVEN MEAN.

17:57.598 --> 18:00.079
I'M SORRY.

18:00.079 --> 18:02.255
I EMBARRASSED
BOTH OF US.

18:02.255 --> 18:04.735
NOT TO MENTION
YOUR DIVORCE LAWYER.

18:04.735 --> 18:07.956
THAT WAS A BAD IDEA.

18:07.956 --> 18:11.742
BUT I DIDN'T KNOW
HOW TO HANDLE YOU

18:11.742 --> 18:13.440
WITHOUT BRINGING
SABRINA ALONG.

18:13.440 --> 18:15.355
WOW.

18:15.355 --> 18:18.053
YOU REALLY WANTED TO MAKE SURE
THERE WAS NO WAY BACK TOGETHER.

18:18.053 --> 18:19.794
MISSION ACCOMPLISHED.

18:19.794 --> 18:21.491
YOU ARE STILL ANGRY.

18:21.491 --> 18:24.103
NO.

18:24.103 --> 18:26.757
SAD.

18:26.757 --> 18:30.065
I SPENT ALL MORNING
WATCHING MYSELF ON VIDEO.

18:30.065 --> 18:32.894
I HATE
WHO I TURNED INTO.

18:32.894 --> 18:34.765
HATE THAT SIDE OF MYSELF.

18:34.765 --> 18:37.986
THIS IS
WHAT TRIALS DO TO YOU.

18:37.986 --> 18:41.816
I'M TRYING TO
SAVE A HUMAN LIFE HERE.

18:41.816 --> 18:44.123
WHAT ABOUT YOUR LIFE?

18:44.123 --> 18:46.125
DID YOU
SLEEP WITH SABRINA YET?

18:46.125 --> 18:49.258
[ CHUCKLES ]
YOU ARE SUCH A LAWYER.

18:49.258 --> 18:52.261
OH, IT DOESN'T MATTER!

18:52.261 --> 18:53.871
IT'S NONE OF MY BUSINESS
ANYMORE.

19:00.095 --> 19:03.881
WE DON'T BRING OUT THE BEST
IN EACH OTHER.

19:03.881 --> 19:06.971
YOU FELT IT
BEFORE I DID.

19:06.971 --> 19:10.018
♪♪

19:15.197 --> 19:17.330
I STILL LOVE YOU.

19:23.249 --> 19:25.686
ME TOO.

19:41.310 --> 19:43.834
DR. MARGARET HOPKINS.

19:43.834 --> 19:46.620
SPELLING --
H-O-P-K-I-N-S.

19:46.620 --> 19:48.883
I AM
A FORENSIC PSYCHIATRIST.

19:48.883 --> 19:53.583
REPEATED CHILD ABUSE,
PHYSICAL AND/OR SEXUAL,

19:53.583 --> 19:56.978
CAN CAUSE A LIFETIME
OF TRAUMATIC STRESS DISORDER

19:56.978 --> 19:58.849
AND DEPRESSION
FOR THE VICTIM.

19:58.849 --> 20:01.461
WHAT ARE THE SYMPTOMS
OF TRAUMATIC STRESS DISORDER

20:01.461 --> 20:03.332
FOR CHILD-ABUSE VICTIMS,
DOCTOR?

20:03.332 --> 20:08.163
DEPRESSION, LONELINESS,
SHAME, SELF-HATRED,

20:08.163 --> 20:12.602
SUICIDAL THOUGHTS,
ANXIETY, AGGRESSION.

20:12.602 --> 20:14.038
I DESCRIBE IT AS

20:14.038 --> 20:19.305
AN OVERARCHING SENSE
OF HOPELESSNESS AND DOOM.

20:19.305 --> 20:23.613
WHEN YOU EVALUATED DUSTIN,
DID YOU NOTE THOSE SYMPTOMS?

20:23.613 --> 20:26.747
YES.
HE HAD ALL OF THEM AND MORE.

20:26.747 --> 20:28.357
WHAT DID YOU CONCLUDE?

20:28.357 --> 20:34.015
I FOUND DUSTIN TO BE
A FRAGILE, MALLEABLE ADOLESCENT,

20:34.015 --> 20:39.194
YOUNG FOR HIS YEARS, EASILY
DOMINATED, CONSISTENT WITH

20:39.194 --> 20:43.154
A HISTORY OF AGGRAVATED
PHYSICAL AND/OR SEXUAL ABUSE

20:43.154 --> 20:44.808
IN EARLY CHILDHOOD.

20:47.898 --> 20:52.903
SO [CLEARS THROAT] YOU HAVE
NO PERSONAL KNOWLEDGE

20:52.903 --> 20:55.645
OF ANY EVIDENCE OF ANY KIND
FROM ANY SOURCE,

20:55.645 --> 20:57.560
INCLUDING
THE DEFENDANT HIMSELF,

20:57.560 --> 21:01.129
THAT HE WAS EVER ACTUALLY
ABUSED IN ANY WAY AT ALL.

21:01.129 --> 21:02.261
ISN'T THAT TRUE,
DOCTOR?

21:02.261 --> 21:04.611
AS A MENTAL-HEALTH EXPERT,

21:04.611 --> 21:06.656
I'M QUALIFIED
TO RECOGNIZE

21:06.656 --> 21:09.311
THE PSYCHOLOGICAL SYMPTOMS
OF TRAUMA.

21:09.311 --> 21:10.834
OH.

21:10.834 --> 21:12.358
ARE YOU QUALIFIED
AS A MIND READER?

21:12.358 --> 21:15.317
OBJECTION. DO I NEED TO SAY
"ARGUMENTATIVE"?

21:15.317 --> 21:17.624
YOUR HONOR, I WAS POSING
A GENUINE QUESTION

21:17.624 --> 21:19.713
ABOUT DR. HOPKINS'
PSYCHIC ABILITIES,

21:19.713 --> 21:21.236
SINCE SHE HAS NO OTHER EVIDENCE
TO SUPPORT HER OPINION.

21:21.236 --> 21:22.629
ENOUGH.
ENOUGH!

21:22.629 --> 21:24.283
ENOUGH!

21:24.283 --> 21:26.023
SUSTAINED.

21:26.023 --> 21:31.768
DOCTOR, DO YOU KNOW OF ANY
SPECIFIC TRAUMA TO THE DEFENDANT

21:31.768 --> 21:34.597
OTHER THAN A BROKEN ARM
DURING SUMMER VACATION?

21:34.597 --> 21:40.734
IT'S NOT UNCOMMON FOR VICTIMS
TO BE UNWILLING OR UNABLE

21:40.734 --> 21:43.650
TO REVEAL THE CAUSE
OR DETAILS.

21:43.650 --> 21:45.913
NO, SEE, MY --
MY QUESTION WAS,

21:45.913 --> 21:48.959
DO YOU KNOWOF ANY
SPECIFIC TRAUMA TO THE DEFENDANT

21:48.959 --> 21:50.613
OTHER THAN
A BROKEN ARM?

21:50.613 --> 21:53.312
NO, I DON'T.

21:53.312 --> 21:55.749
THANK YOU, DOCTOR.

21:57.577 --> 22:01.276
THE DEFENSE
CALLS DUSTIN MAKER.

22:01.276 --> 22:04.410
[ SPECTATORS MURMUR ]

22:13.375 --> 22:17.336
WE KNOW WHO DIED,
AND WE KNOW WHO KILLED THEM.

22:17.336 --> 22:19.599
WE KNOW WHERE
AND WHEN AND HOW.

22:19.599 --> 22:21.470
NOW IT'S TIME TO LEARN
WHY.

22:21.470 --> 22:27.389
WHY DID YOU AND ALFRED RENTMAN
SHOOT 18 PEOPLE?

22:27.389 --> 22:30.827
ALFRED
WANTED US TO BE LEGENDS.

22:30.827 --> 22:32.829
HE SAID
NO ONE WOULD FORGET OUR NAMES.

22:32.829 --> 22:35.266
DID YOU
WANT TO BE A LEGEND?

22:35.266 --> 22:36.529
IT WAS OKAY.

22:36.529 --> 22:40.010
I JUST WANTED EVERYTHING
OVER AND OUT.

22:40.010 --> 22:42.143
BY "EVERYTHING"
MEANING...?

22:42.143 --> 22:45.886
MY WHOLE STUPID,
MISERABLE LIFE.

22:47.322 --> 22:51.239
I WANTED TO DIE.

22:51.239 --> 22:53.284
I NEEDED MY BRAIN
TO STOP.

22:53.284 --> 22:55.809
IS THAT WHY YOU TRIED TO
SHOOT YOURSELF IN THE HEAD

22:55.809 --> 22:57.637
RIGHT BEFORE
THE POLICE SHOT YOU?

22:57.637 --> 23:00.335
YEAH.
[ SIGHS ]

23:00.335 --> 23:03.860
IF MY GUN HADN'T JAMMED,
I'D BE GONE, LIKE ALFIE.

23:03.860 --> 23:06.689
WE WERE BOTH
SUPPOSED TO DIE.

23:06.689 --> 23:10.345
THEN WHY DID YOU WEAR
BULLETPROOF VESTS?

23:10.345 --> 23:14.262
ALFIE SAID KEVLAR WOULD
GIVE US MORE GAME TIME.

23:14.262 --> 23:17.134
DO YOU KNOW WHAT HE MEANT
BY "GAME TIME"?

23:17.134 --> 23:18.788
IT'S JUST
HOW HE TALKED.

23:18.788 --> 23:22.357
I DIDN'T ALWAYS
UNDERSTAND IT, BUT...

23:22.357 --> 23:25.316
GUESS I DIDN'T HAVE TO.

23:25.316 --> 23:28.711
WERE YOU BULLIED AT SCHOOL,
DUSTIN?

23:28.711 --> 23:31.714
EVERYONE GETS BULLIED
AT SOME POINT.

23:31.714 --> 23:33.542
IT'S NOT WHY I DID IT.

23:33.542 --> 23:35.457
DO YOU KNOW WHY?

23:35.457 --> 23:39.243
THEY WERE HAPPY.

23:39.243 --> 23:41.724
TALKING AND LAUGHING.

23:44.510 --> 23:46.773
TALKING AND LAUGHING...

23:49.602 --> 23:53.780
...ALL THE TIME
ABOUT NOTHING.

23:53.780 --> 23:56.870
WITH THEIR BABY FACES.

23:56.870 --> 23:59.699
SO CLEAN.

23:59.699 --> 24:01.265
SO IGNORANT.

24:01.265 --> 24:04.965
THEY COULDN'T SEE ME.

24:04.965 --> 24:08.838
THEY DIDN'T KNOW ME.

24:08.838 --> 24:10.797
[ HANDCUFFS RATTLE ]

24:10.797 --> 24:15.541
THEY DIDN'T WANT TO.

24:15.541 --> 24:19.458
IT WAS LIKE THEY LIVED IN
A WHOLE NOTHER COUNTRY

24:19.458 --> 24:20.981
THAT I
COULDN'T EVEN VISIT.

24:20.981 --> 24:23.374
WHERE KIDS
DIDN'T GET ABUSED?

24:23.374 --> 24:25.594
THAT DIDN'T HAPPEN TO ME.

24:25.594 --> 24:27.030
I D--
I NEVER SAID THAT.

24:27.030 --> 24:28.902
HOW DID YOU
BREAK YOUR ARM?

24:28.902 --> 24:31.905
I DON'T REMEMBER.
I WAS LIKE 6.

24:31.905 --> 24:33.384
DID YOUR PARENTS
SEND YOU BACK

24:33.384 --> 24:35.169
TO STAY WITH YOUR UNCLE
AND YOUR COUSINS

24:35.169 --> 24:37.388
EVERY SUMMER AFTER THAT
UNTIL YOU WERE 12?

24:37.388 --> 24:38.955
YEAH.

24:38.955 --> 24:42.263
WHEN YOU WERE FINALLY
BIG ENOUGH TO DEFEND YOURSELF?

24:44.831 --> 24:46.659
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

24:46.659 --> 24:49.313
DID YOUR COUSIN DAISY
HAVE THE ROOM NEXT TO YOU?

24:49.313 --> 24:51.141
SO WHAT?

24:51.141 --> 24:54.536
AND WAS YOUR UNCLE'S ROOM AT THE
END OF THE HALL -- UNCLE BEAU?

24:57.191 --> 24:58.627
I DON'T REMEMBER.

24:58.627 --> 25:01.021
DO YOU REMEMBER
WALKING PAST DAISY'S ROOM

25:01.021 --> 25:02.892
WHEN YOUR UNCLE
WOULD CALL FOR YOU?

25:02.892 --> 25:05.547
N-NO.

25:05.547 --> 25:08.115
WHAT WOULD DAISY
SAY ABOUT THAT?

25:08.115 --> 25:11.118
WHAT DID DAISY SEE
EVERY SUMMER

25:11.118 --> 25:12.598
THAT YOU'RE
NOT TELLING US, DUSTIN?

25:14.774 --> 25:16.645
YOU KNOW WHAT SHE SAW.

25:16.645 --> 25:18.778
SHE'S LYING.
I MEAN, SHE'S A LIAR.

25:18.778 --> 25:20.954
SHE WOULDN'T HAVE
SEEN ANYTHING.

25:20.954 --> 25:22.390
N-NOTHING EVER HAPPENED
IN THE HOUSE, FOR --

25:22.390 --> 25:23.609
BECAUSE YOUR UNCLE
ALWAYS TOOK YOU

25:23.609 --> 25:25.262
TO THE MACHINE SHOP,
DIDN'T HE?

25:25.262 --> 25:28.744
WHERE HE THOUGHT YOUR COUSINS
WOULDN'T HEAR YOU CRY.

25:28.744 --> 25:30.616
I HARDLY EVER CRIED.

25:36.230 --> 25:39.102
[ Voice breaking ]
I HARDLY EVER CRIED.

25:39.102 --> 25:42.541
I CAN'T SIT HERE
AND LISTEN TO THIS.

25:42.541 --> 25:44.978
Riley:
LYDIA, SIT DOWN.

25:44.978 --> 25:48.764
[ Voice breaking ] YOU STAY
IF YOU WANT TO STAY.

25:48.764 --> 25:50.810
WOULD YOU MOVE?

25:50.810 --> 25:53.639
[ SPECTATORS MURMURING ]

25:53.639 --> 25:56.642
♪♪

26:05.346 --> 26:08.001
[ BREATHES DEEPLY ]

26:12.788 --> 26:14.311
I DON'T WANT TO BE HERE.

26:14.311 --> 26:17.227
I'M NOT
SUPPOSED TO BE HERE.

26:17.227 --> 26:20.535
THE PLAN WAS TO DIE
WITH EVERYBODY ELSE.

26:20.535 --> 26:24.191
BUT ALFRED DIDN'T
FOLLOW THE PLAN, DID HE?

26:24.191 --> 26:27.411
I THOUGHT WE'D AGREED.

26:27.411 --> 26:29.718
DID YOU KNOW
HE WAS GONNA TRY TO ESCAPE?

26:29.718 --> 26:31.372
NO.

26:31.372 --> 26:34.897
DID YOU KNOW HE WAS GONNA
TAKE BARBIE SANFORD HOSTAGE?

26:34.897 --> 26:36.507
NO.

26:36.507 --> 26:38.509
DID YOU KNOW HE WAS GOING TO
THE POINT BONITA LIGHTHOUSE?

26:38.509 --> 26:40.250
NO.

26:40.250 --> 26:43.123
YOU WEREN'T PART OF
ALFRED'S BIGGER PLAN, WERE YOU?

26:45.038 --> 26:46.430
I DIDN'T KNOW
HE HAD ONE.

26:46.430 --> 26:48.215
WHEN ALFRED
DIDN'T NEED YOU ANYMORE,

26:48.215 --> 26:52.306
HE LEFT YOU BEHIND,
DIDN'T HE?

26:54.177 --> 26:59.008
[ Voice breaking ]
HE...GOT TO DIE.

27:03.796 --> 27:06.363
AND I'M STILL HERE.

27:08.409 --> 27:12.021
AND I DON'T
UNDERSTAND WHY.

27:12.021 --> 27:18.071
DUSTIN, ARE YOU SORRY
ABOUT WHAT YOU DID ON THE BUS?

27:27.733 --> 27:30.910
EVERY SECOND...

27:30.910 --> 27:33.608
OF EVERY MINUTE...

27:33.608 --> 27:36.524
OF EVERY DAY...

27:36.524 --> 27:39.614
FOR AS LONG
