THE ONLY VOICE THE DEAD HAVE
HERE AND NOW IS MINE,

33:32.401 --> 33:34.447
AND THE ONLY SENTENCE
THAT ACKNOWLEDGES

33:34.447 --> 33:38.755
THE LOSS OF THEIR HOPES,
