33:38.755 --> 33:42.846
IS THE ULTIMATE SANCTION
ON THE MAN RESPONSIBLE.

33:42.846 --> 33:44.979
IT'S TIME TO RESPECT THE DEAD,
YOUR HONOR.

33:44.979 --> 33:47.503
IT IS TIME TO GIVE THEM
THE JUSTICE THEY DESERVE.

33:48.765 --> 33:51.942
SENTENCE THIS MAN TO DEATH

33:51.942 --> 33:56.077
FOR THE MONSTROUS CRIMES
