BE BROUGHT TO HUMAN JUSTICE.

34:28.327 --> 34:33.375
ONLY THE DAMAGED,
IMMATURE 18-YEAR-OLD

34:33.375 --> 34:36.552
HE MANIPULATED INTO HELPING HIM
